en_572119_0	Western province-based 8 Sri Lanka Light Infantry (SLLI) troops of the 141 Brigade under the 14 Division of the Security Force Headquarters-West as one more of their routine community projects, visited the YMBA-managed Elders' Home at Udupila, Kelaniya on Monday (29) and attended to the timely needs of those inmates.
en_572119_1	At first, troops cleaned up the surroundings and bathed all the inmates after shaving them thoroughly and cutting their hair with the support given by members of the staff.
en_572119_2	Afterwards, all of them were provided with refreshments and a hearty lunch.
en_572119_3	Commanding Officer, Senior Officers and Other Ranks took part in the social service project.
